      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be safely roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly with a noticeable knocking sound, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the body shows significant rust on the wheel wells and several deep scratches and dents throughout. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics, making this an ideal project car for someone looking to do a full restoration.",
